titleNullable: Parts Revenue from Automotive Industry Dealer
subtitleNullable: Parts Sales Revenue per day from a single automotive dealer workshop
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset is a result of a simple SQL query directly from an Automotive Dealer Workshop database showing the Parts Revenue per day.
The dataset has the following characteristics:
Date Start: 2007-12-31
Date End: 2021-03-12

### Content

Each row represents one day and its parts revenue for the given date.
The dataset has the following characteristics:
-Has no missing values (null) but has 66 null values (zero)
|Date|Nulls|
| --- | --- |
|Mon|4|
|Tue|1|
|Wed|3|
|Thu|1|
|Fri|0|
|Sat|30|
|Sun|27|

-Has missing dates in between
Dataset period should have 4821 days, but it has 3156 days, resulting at 65% ratio
If the dataset will be imputed by zeros on the  missing days then more missing values (zeros) are present
|Date|Nulls|
| --- | --- |
|Mon|77|
|Tue|57|
|Wed|57|
|Thu|51|
|Fri|70|
|Sat|663|
|Sun|668|

-Has negative values
Total negative date - values are 19 because of:
--credited invoices on days where no invoice had taken place
--credited invoces  amount exceeds the invoice amount of a given day

### Observations
-for most of the weekends, technicians usually do not work over the weekend
-for random days within a week, the workshop may not invoice some days because of no visits
-for public holidays within a week, the workshop may not invoice some days because of no visits
